                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The accursed forge-spurned has used Forge Breath.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The accursed forge-spurned re-inflates its flaccid lungs, enabling it to use Forge Breath again.</p>"
